short_desc: IF INRELTO=1 then INLIVWTH should not equal 0
full_desc: IF Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant)=1 (spouse, partner, companion), then Q3. INLIVWTH (lives with participant?) should not equal 0 (no)

test_name: INLIVWTH compared to participants living situation
short_desc: IF INLIVWTH=1 then LIVSITUA cannot equal 1
full_desc: IF Q4. INLIVWTH (lives with participant?)=1 (yes) then Form A1, Q12. LIVSITUA (participant's living situation) should not equal 1 (lives alone)

short_desc: IF NEWINF=0 and INRELTO[prev_vis]=2, then INRELTO should =2
full_desc: IF Q1. NEWINF (new co-participant?)=0 (No) and INRELTO (relationship to participant)=2 (Child) at the previous UDS visit, then Q2. INRELTO (relationship to participant) should equal 2 (Child)
test_logic: IF (NEWINF=0 and INRELTO[prev_vis]=2) and INRELTO ne 2

short_desc: IF NEWINF=0 and INRELTO[prev_vis]=3, then INRELTO should =3
full_desc: IF Q1. NEWINF (new co-participant?)=0 (No) and INRELTO (relationship to participant)=3 (Sibling) at the previous UDS visit, then Q2. INRELTO (relationship to participant) should equal 3 (Sibling)
test_logic: IF (NEWINF=0 and INRELTO[prev_vis]=3) and INRELTO ne 3
